Name: Territory
Desc: Creates a personal domain to create countless swords. This skill doesn't affect enemies in the Damage Reflection status.

H.Old:
MP Cost: 120. Creates a domain which periodically attacks up to 8 enemies at 100% damage 4 times for 7 sec.
After the duration ends, all swords turn around to attack up to 12 enemies at 550% damage 12 times.
Cooldown: 30 sec.
